# ─── Google Sign-In OAuth Client IDs ─────────────────────────────────────────
# To enable Google sign-in:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/ → APIs & Services → Credentials
# 2. Create OAuth 2.0 Client IDs for:
#    - Web application   → paste below as WEB and ANDROID values
#    - iOS               → paste below as IOS value
# 3. For Android: add your SHA-1 fingerprint from `cd android && ./gradlew signingReport`
# 4. Restart the Expo bundler after changing these values
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID=956886937569-s0db9qdqbkrgvpid8tv6179h17260bi5.apps.googleusercontent.com
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_IOS_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID=

